<HEADLINE> Tehran Stock Exchange Index Down </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
TEHRAN, July 31 (Xinhua) -- The general price index at Tehran
Stock Exchange on Saturday closed at 1701.42 points, down 22.85
points from Wednesday's finish.
</P>
<P>
A total of 884,360 shares changed hands in 677 turns and the
turnover stood at 2.48 billion rials (about 826,000 U.S. dollars).
</P>
<P>
The shares of 25 companies made gains while those of 17 others
declined. 
</P>
</TEXT>
