<P>
BONN, August 1 (Xinhua) -- Eddie Irvine took away the title at
the German Grand Prix, seizing the lead in the Formula One
championship and leading Ferrari to a spectacular 1-2 finish in
Hockenheim of Germany on Sunday.
</P>
