had a long pit stop on lap 24 that dropped him from the lead to
fourth place and then blew his rear left tire to crash out of the
race in the 26th lap.
</P>
<P>
Hakkinen's car careened into a protective tire barrier. The
Finn walked away from the accident but appeared to have some
facial bruises. 
