kilometers further north -- areas along the border with China's
Tibet.
</P>
<P>
There was no immediate report of damage.
</P>
<P>
Panday said that there was a quake of about 5 degrees magnitude
about three months ago in the area near the present epicenter
area.
</P>
<P>
Earthquakes measuring four and five on the Richer scale are
powerful enough to cause heavy damages in populated areas.
