<HEADLINE> Zambian President Urges Africans to Resolve Own </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
LUSAKA, August 1 (Xinhua) -- Zambia President Frederick Chiluba
has called on Africans to work together towards finding solutions
for problems besetting the continent.
</P>
<P>
