<HEADLINE> Possible Doping Offense Occurs at Pan Am Games </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
WINNIPEG, Canada, July 31 (Xinhua) -- The Canadian Olympic
Association (COA) confirmed here today that it received
notification from the Pan Am Sports Organization (PASO) of a
positive doping test involving a Canadian athlete.
</P>
<P>
